{
  "stem": "748.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the front came always near.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and they brought food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mine God, it's like the-- everything looked like black coffee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- and hunger is not, I will not eat this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We eat this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And who didn't-- who didn't-- can't eat, didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was a big crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] they schlepped the people what's dead, [INAUDIBLE], like, you know, dogs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted bread?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Put this in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They should-- they was on the street and every place-- dead people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That a human being is just like a animal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes, when we go out in the night, you know, to the bathroom or so, and there wasn't a dead person is, oh, they didn't put any here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have to go in-- in-- in the-- in-- in-- in the dirt.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you know, so selfish you was, you fight for your life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is un-possible that, normal, a person can do it this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But sometimes, in Auschwitz, there was a lot of [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] soldiers from the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they used to bring bread and a salami, and they threw on the-- on-- on-- on-- on the [NON-ENGLISH] where we sleeped.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they just say, share with another one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One parcel, I got from this friend from my mother, a Polish man, Jwardzik.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got three daughters.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- every summer, I used the come to them on the farm, my mother and me, and my, sometimes, father came in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One parcel, I got.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, a-- a Catholic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't send of my name, because I could write a letter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sent of Ilka's name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she got-- she was from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
